The paper focuses on image generation using deep convolutional GANs, which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a novel architecture for conditional GANs, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper discusses the generation of images with multiple objects, which involves spatial relationships and occlusions, making it relevant to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
